videos.description: Nathan Elliott lobs one to Anthony Ratliff-Williams who makes a ridiculous, juggling catch for 40-yard gain.
videos.headline: Ratliff-Williams makes acrobatic catch

videos.description: Nathan Elliott hit Brandon Fritts to extend the Tar Heels' early lead.
videos.headline: Elliott fires a TD strike to Fritts for UNC

videos.description: Darrin Hall blasts through the hole for the 7-yard score.
videos.headline: Hall powers in for Pitt

videos.description: Maurice Ffrench uses his speed to on a jet sweep to set up the Pittsburgh touchdown on the next play.
videos.headline: Ffrench takes sweep to the 1-yard line

videos.description: WR Anthony Ratliff-Williams finds a wide open Josh Cabrera for the score on the trick play.
videos.headline: UNC scores TD on double-reverse pass

videos.description: Quadree Henderson fumbles on the one-yard line and Cayson Collins returns it 66 yards to set up UNC.
videos.headline: UNC forces fumble on the 1-yard line

videos.description: Head coach Larry Fedora likes how his offense is playing despite a few miscues and says they have to keep up the energy.
videos.headline: Fedora likes UNC's first half effort

videos.description: Darrin Hall rumbles in for the 9-yard score to tie the game.
videos.headline: Pittsburgh's Hall scores third TD of game

videos.description: Pittsburgh RB Darrin Hall scores on another physical run to give the Panthers the lead.
videos.headline: Hall runs it in for his fourth TD

videos.description: Head coach Larry Fedora is proud of how his third-string QB took care of the ball as the Tar Heels get their first ACC win of the year.
videos.headline: UNC's Fedora proud of his team's fight
